<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph>
Essential DocIO has the functionality to convert key document formats, including HTML to Word, Word to HTML, Word to PDF, Word to RTF, and RTF to Word.
</Paragraph>
<Paragraph><Bold>Word to EPub</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting a Word document as an EPub document.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>Word to HTML</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting a Word document as HTML document. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>Word to PDF</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's and Essential PDF's support for converting a Word document as a PDF file. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>Word to RTF</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting a Word document as an RTF file. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>HTML to Word</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting HTML document as a Word document. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>RTF to Word</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting an RTF file as a Word document.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>Word to Image</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting Word document as Image files. </Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
<Bold>Word to ODT</Bold> - This sample demonstrates Essential DocIO's support for converting Word document as an ODT document. </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>




